## TOPs Frameset Meshes to OBJ Mesh Sequence

### Example HIP:

* TOPs_Frameset_Meshes_to_OBJ_Mesh_Sequence_V001.hip

### Description:

Copy the Reality Capture generated OBJ mesh files and texture maps from their initial numbered frameset folders into a common"mesh" folder. This allows the mesh sequence data to be played back as a linear volumetric video sequence.

### TOPs Node Parameters:
